00:00:21.300 --> 00:00:26.700
Episode 21 - Im Restaurant 

00:00:27.840 --> 00:00:32.540
A table for two please.

00:00:33.100 --> 00:00:37.360
Ein Tisch für Zwei, bitte. 

00:00:38.120 --> 00:00:42.420
Is this table free?

00:00:43.160 --> 00:00:47.740
Ist der Tisch frei?

00:00:48.380 --> 00:00:52.980
I would like the menu, please.

00:00:53.680 --> 00:00:57.440
Die Karte, bitte.

00:00:58.040 --> 00:01:02.920
What are today's specials?

00:01:03.720 --> 00:01:09.040
Was sind die Tagesangebote heute?

00:01:09.780 --> 00:01:14.320
We would like to order.

00:01:15.020 --> 00:01:19.360
Wir würden gern bestellen.

00:01:19.920 --> 00:01:24.440
What would you recommend?

00:01:25.040 --> 00:01:29.360
Was würden Sie empfehlen?

00:01:30.020 --> 00:01:35.080
Do you have vegetarian dishes?

00:01:35.740 --> 00:01:40.500
Haben Sie vegetarische Gerichte?

00:01:41.360 --> 00:01:46.440
Can we please have the wine card?

00:01:47.080 --> 00:01:52.300
Könnten wir bitte die Weinkarte haben.

00:01:52.860 --> 00:01:57.380
I would like the steak.

00:01:58.120 --> 00:02:02.500
Ich nehme das Steak.

00:02:03.080 --> 00:02:07.160
I will take the schnitzel.

00:02:07.740 --> 00:02:12.520
Ich neheme das Schnitzel.

00:02:13.360 --> 00:02:17.840
Can I please have the bill?

00:02:18.380 --> 00:02:23.260
Kann ich bitte die Rechnung bekommen.

00:02:24.000 --> 00:02:28.400
Can I pay with credit card?

00:02:28.980 --> 00:02:33.940
Kann ich mit Kreditkarte bezahlen?

